com.misc.common.moplaf.solver

Interface Solver

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, IGeneratorTool, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, SolutionProvider
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    SolverCp, SolverLp
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SolverCpImpl, SolverImpl, SolverLpImpl

    public interface Solver
extends SolutionProvider
    A representation of the model object 'Solver'. A Solver is the common implementation of a concrete solver, that must implement the method solverLp()

    The following features are supported:

    • Remarks
    • Status
    • Solver Max Duration
    • Solver Background
    • Sol Value
    • Solver Log Level
    • Solver Dump
    • Run Started
    • Run Initialization Ended
    • Run Solving Ended
    • Run Finalization Ended
    • Run Duration Initialization
    • Run Duration Finalization
    • Run Duration Solving
    • Run Request Terminate
    • Sol Unfeasible
    • Sol Feasible
    • Sol Optimal
    • Run Interrupted
    • Solving
    • Finalizing
    • Finished
    • Run Time Out
    • Initializing
    See Also:
    SolverPackage.getSolver()
